            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>數據狗(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:DDOG:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/DDOG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">DDOG-US</a>)截至台北時間15日21:35股價上漲6.22美元，報116.79美元，漲幅5.62%，成交量227,435（股），盤中最高價116.83美元、最低價112.45美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.26%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.29%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+0.33%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：-0.24%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>數據狗(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:DDOG:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/DDOG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">DDOG-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-5.12%</li> <li>近 1 月：-11.2%</li> <li>近 3 月：-9.67%</li> <li>近 6 月：-31.27%</li> <li>今年以來：-18.69%</li></ul></section></main>",
